title: #92Noon! Fenton & Boudreau put Wild to rest
description: Nordo was at the NCAA Title game last night...Mike Florio was too and he joined PA first hour. Midway through is the season ending presser for the Wild featuring Paul Fenton and Bruce Boudreau...Lynx coach/GM Cheryl Reeve is on the hotline before tomorrow's WNBA draft, and more!
